sentences.english: Those initially treated operatively, or who died before follow-up were excluded.
sentences.chinese: 除外接受手术治疗者和随访期内死亡者。

sentences.english: The window is never open except in summer.
sentences.chinese: 这扇窗户从来不开，夏季除外。

sentences.english: Category includes hand molders &shapers except jewelers.
sentences.chinese: 包括手工铸模&刨床，珠宝匠除外。

sentences.english: Parentheses: trades women and peddlers excepted.
Chemical wood pulp, sulphite, other than dissolving grades.
sentences.chinese: 亚硫酸盐木浆，但溶解级的除外。

sentences.english: There are no known exceptions and exclusions at the time this document was created.
sentences.chinese: 在创建本文档之时还没有已知的例外与除外责任。

sentences.english: Except for one day, and that was the section from Basu to Changdu.
sentences.chinese: 但有一天除外，那就是从八宿到昌都的路。

sentences.english: There are many things which can make you popular with others except fashion.
sentences.chinese: 有许多事情能使您与别的流行时装除外。

sentences.english: Don't stay in bed longer than a day or two unless your docter advises it.
sentences.chinese: 卧床最好不要超过一到两天，医嘱除外。

sentences.english: They'll all lie. Leastways all but the nigger.
sentences.chinese: 他们都在撒谎，那个黑人可能除外。

sentences.english: I don't really miss anything though, except family and friends, of course.
sentences.chinese: 那里没有任何东西令我挂念，当然家人和朋友除外。

sentences.english: Except as otherwise provided by law.
Patients with generalized peritonitis and a history of abdominal surgery were excluded.
sentences.chinese: 有弥漫性腹膜炎和既往腹部手术史者除外。

sentences.english: Chemical wood pulp, soda or sulphate, other than dissolving grades.
sentences.chinese: 碱木浆或硫酸盐木浆，但溶解级的除外。

sentences.english: Except for Zen Habits. That’s the only blog you’re allowed to read when you decompress.
sentences.chinese: 禅那网除外，当你减压时只允许读这个博客。
